        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 2 at 5:26PM CDT until June 2 at 5:45PM CDT by NWS Sioux Falls SD</headline>
        <description>At 525 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Vermillion,
moving east at 30 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Hail damage to vehicles is expected. Expect wind damage to
roofs, siding, and trees.

This severe storm will be near...
Union Grove State Park around 530 PM CDT.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
